{"tid":1756634,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【深水埗潮州粉面店 不招待黑警/強姦犯/殺人犯】","createTime":"2019-11-26T06:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T08:55:59.000Z","uid":162969,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e10ec29a1020713a2cae918ecdaa46d5ad617215","tid":1756634,"uid":162969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hrRn9JG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhrRn9JG.jpg&h=1e727e3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GBfLg2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GBfLg2.jpg&h=386fc2d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n位於深水埗的呢間潮州粉面店，緊跟區選潮流，今日推出「何已完」節慶贈飲，又指「黑警」、「強姦犯」、「殺人犯」，「都係一樣者，總之不招待，請自重。」<br />\n<br />\n該店又設有「捍衛我城學生餐」，憑學生證可以免費享用至「光復之日」、「本店結業」。<br />\n<br />\n寸寸貢的老闆歡迎大家「留返條命食窮」佢。<br />\n<br />\n攝影：Ming<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1432983410299343/posts/2444839762447031?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1432983410299343%2Fposts%2F2444839762447031%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04CLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=c6361750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1432983410299343/posts/2444839762447031?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"2b3463d223d5e808d4dd19665307e91c55596e1b","tid":1756634,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10dda7aa11feb8e7eeff7f6ddc62aa5861ff9219","tid":1756634,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:27:21.000Z","msg":"係咪以前旺角嗰間<br />\n<br />\n近而家新寶戲院"},{"pid":"e267ba8aa0dc86eecec3d6439f7d657cfa298c01","tid":1756634,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:27:52.000Z","msg":"深水埗標記藍到黑 想扮黃？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ewDA